<body>
<div type="letter">
<pb facs="1063217" n="1"/> 
  <opener><lb/><salute>Viro Illustrissimo <abbr>atq.</abbr> Doctissimo
      <lb/><rs type="person">Nicolao Bernoulli</rs>
      <lb/><abbr>S. P. D.</abbr>
      <lb/><rs type="person">Johannes Checotius</rs>.</salute> </opener>
<p><lb/>Quominus Frater meus <rs type="person">Sebastianus</rs> <rs type="letter">litteris</rs> tuis respondeat, <abbr>Cel.</abbr> Vir, in
  <lb/>cau<unclear>ss</unclear>a est difficilis et periculosus morbus, qui et ill<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> lecto affigit,
  <lb/>et me angore ingenti, incredibilique maerore dejcit. Cum igitur
  <lb/><rs type="person">Frater</rs> ne legere quidem postremas tuas <rs type="letter">litteras</rs> quiverit, sumsi ego
  <lb/>negocium respondendi, quod quidem ad officium pertinet, nam quae<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>stiones de quibus inter vos disputatis, cum illae extra fines meae
  <lb/>Provinciae sint, attingendas mihi non arbitror. Quod si Misericors
  <lb/>Deus annuere votis nostris volet, illumque, pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ograv">ò</g></orig><reg>o</reg></choice> immensa bonitate sua,
  <lb/>propinquis et necessariis incolumem restituere, non dubito<del>[...]</del> quin <rs type="person">Fratri</rs>
  <lb/>gratissimam fortunam sit de rebus Geometri<del>[...]</del><add>c</add>is, quas in delicijs habere
  <lb/>solitus est, tecum amice disserere. Nam quanta iste, Vir <abbr>Cel.</abbr>, observan<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>tia prosequatur, quantique doctrinam tuam faciat, testis ego certissimus
  <lb/>esse possum. Interim, in summa tristitia, gaudeo me quoque nactum
  <lb/>esse tempus ostendendi tibi magnitudinem observantiae erga te meae. </p>
  <closer>Vale.
    <lb/><dateline>Dabam <rs type="place">Vicentiae</rs> Die <date when="1719-06-20">20 Junij 1719.</date></dateline>
